355/*******************************************************************************
356 *
357 * FUNCTION: AcpiAhMatchPredefinedName
358 *
359 * PARAMETERS: Nameseg - Predefined name string
360 *
361 * RETURN: ID info struct. NULL if Nameseg not found
362 *
363 * DESCRIPTION: Lookup a predefined name.
364 *
365 ******************************************************************************/
366
367const AH_PREDEFINED_NAME *
368AcpiAhMatchPredefinedName (
369 char *Nameseg)
370{
371 const AH_PREDEFINED_NAME *Info;
372
373
374 /* Nameseg must start with an underscore */
375
376 if (*Nameseg != '_')
377 {
378 return (NULL);
379 }
380
381 /* Search for a match in the predefined name table */
382
383 for (Info = AslPredefinedInfo; Info->Name; Info++)
384 {
385 if (ACPI_COMPARE_NAMESEG (Nameseg, Info->Name))
386 {
387 return (Info);
388 }
389 }
390
391 return (NULL);
392}
